file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description:  |
    [https://www.veryfi.com/](https://www.veryfi.com/).
  version: "7.0.0"
  title: Verify API
  contact:
    email: support@veryfi.com
  license:
    name: MIT
    url: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/veryfi/veryfi-python/master/LICENSE'
    
servers:
  - url: 'https://api.veryfi.com/api/v7/partner/'
  
tags:
  - name: documents
    description: Operations with documents.
  - name: line-items
    description: Operations with line items.
  - name: tags
    description: Operations with tags.
    
security:
  - ClientId: []
  - Authorization: []
  
paths:
  /documents:
    get:
      tags:
        - documents
      summary: Get Documents or Search Documents.
      operationId: getDocuments
      description: |
        Return list of previously processed documents or retrieve all the documents matching specified filters.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Query'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Tag'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/ExternalId'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/CreatedGte'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/CreatedGt'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/CreatedLte'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/CreatedLt'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Documents'
                  
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
    post:
      tags:
        - documents
      summary: Process a Document.
      operationId: processDocument
      description: |
        Process a document and extract all the fields from it.
        
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/DocumentUploadOptions'
        
      responses:
        '201':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Document'
                  
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
          
  /documents/{document_id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - documents
      summary: Get a Document.
      operationId: getDocument
      description: |
        Retrieve a existing document by ID.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/ReturnAuditTrail'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Document'
                  
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
    put:
      tags:
        - documents
      summary: Update a Document.
      operationId: updateDocument
      description: |
        Update data for a previously processed document, including almost any field like `vendor`, `date`, `notes` and etc.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/Document'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Document'
                  
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
    delete:
      tags:
        - documents
      summary: Delete a Document.
      operationId: deleteDocument
      description: |
        Delete an existing document by ID.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
         
  /documents/{document_id}/line-items:
    get:
      tags:
        - line-items
      summary: Get Line Items.
      operationId: getLineItems
      description: |
        Retrieve all line items for a specific document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/LineItems'
          
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
    post:
      tags:
        - line-items
      summary: Add a Line Item.
      operationId: addLineItem
      description: |
        Add a new line item on an existing document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/LineItem'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/LineItem'
          
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
    delete:
      tags:
        - line-items
      summary: Delete All Line Items.
      operationId: deleteAllLineItems
      description: |
        Delete all line items on an existing document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
  /documents/{document_id}/line-items/{line_item_id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - line-items
      summary: Get a Line Item.
      operationId: getLineItem
      description: |
        Retrieve a line item for existing document by ID.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/LineItemId'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/LineItem'
          
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
       
    put:
      tags:
        - line-items
      summary: Update a Line Item.
      operationId: updateLineItem
      description: |
        Update an existing line item on an existing document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/LineItemId'
        
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/LineItem'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/LineItem'
          
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
       
    delete:
      tags:
        - line-items
      summary: Delete a Line Item.
      operationId: deleteLineItem
      description: |
        Delete an existing line item on an existing document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/LineItemId'
        
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
  /tags:
    get:
      tags:
        - tags
      summary: Get Tags.
      operationId: getTags
      description: |
        Retrieve all existing tags.
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Tags'
                  
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
  /tags/{tag_id}:
    delete:
      tags:
        - tags
      summary: Delete a Tag.
      operationId: deleteTag
      description: |
        Delete a tag globally. The tag will be removed from all documents.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/TagId'
        
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
  /documents/{document_id}/tags:
    get:
      tags:
        - tags
      summary: Get Document Tags.
      operationId: getDocumentTags
      description: |
        Retrieve all tags for a specific document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Tags'
          
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
    put:
      tags:
        - tags
      summary: Add a Document Tag.
      operationId: addDocumentTag
      description: |
        Add a new tag on an existing document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/Tag'
        
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Tag'
          
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
    delete:
      tags:
        - tags
      summary: Delete All Document Tags.
      operationId: deleteAllDocumentTags
      description: |
        Delete all tags from an existing document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
  /documents/{document_id}/tags/{tag_id}:
    delete:
      tags:
        - tags
      summary: Delete a Document Tag.
      operationId: deleteDocumentTag
      description: |
        Delete a tag from an existing document.
        
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/DocumentId'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/TagId'
        
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OperationStatus'
          
components:
  schemas:
    Tag:
      type: object
      required:
      - id
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 75788890
        name:
          type: string
          example: 'tag'
          
    TaxLine:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          example: 'SALES'
        order:
          type: integer
          example: 0
        base:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 1.11
        rate:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 1.11
        total:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 2.22
          
    LineItem:
      type: object
      required:
      - id
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 75788890
        date:
          type: string
          example: ''
        description:
          type: string
          example: '98 Meat Pty Xchz'
        discount:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 0.0
        end_date:
          type: string
          example: ''
        hsn:
          type: string
          example: ''
        order:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        price:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 12.50
        quantity:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 1.0
        reference:
          type: string
          example: ''
        section:
          type: string
          example: ''
        sku:
          type: string
          example: '038902058959'
        start_date:
          type: string
          example: ''
        tags:
          type: array
          items:
           $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tag'
        tax:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 7.66
        tax_rate:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 7.66
        total:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 88.2
        type:
          type: string
          example: 'food'
        unit_of_measure:
          type: string
          example: ''
          
    Document:
      type: object
      required:
      - id
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 38947300
        abn_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        account_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        bill_to_address:
          type: string
          example: '2 Court Square\nNew York, NY 12210'
        bill_to_name:
          type: string
          example: 'John Smith'
        bill_to_vat_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        card_number:
          type: string
          example: '7373'
        cashback:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 7.66
        category:
          type: string
          example: 'Meals & Entertainment'
        created:
          type: string
          example: '2021-08-05 17:24:48'
        currency_code:
          type: string
          example: 'USD'
        date:
          type: string
          example: '2021-08-05 10:24:48'
        delivery_date:
          type: string
          example: ''
        discount:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 7.66
        document_reference_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        document_title:
          type: string
          example: 'INVOICE'
        document_type:
          type: string
          example: 'invoice'
        due_date:
          type: string
          example: '2019-02-26'
        duplicate_of:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          nullable: true
          example: 38995348
        external_id:
          type: string
          example: ''
        img_file_name:
          type: string
          example: '8247b18a-41f0-443c-bbf4-10814385e097.pdf'
        img_thumbnail_url:
          type: string
          example: 'https://scdn.veryfi.com/receipts/470e7ab9-3084-4d05-b840-885383a2c22e/thumbnail.jpg?Expires=1628185188&Signature=cnyZCF~GnF2TkizYWObnGuNDhmkCsRl5-XoVymoalJFjJCrQKmq7RbpS6RCUnt60aVlPiT1uJeQJXG4eyZOg~FfJc5-ieC0gkqAFhh9vCRjzph15niTfq0mKg23nOu3YR8BJcWBfPfEL8k3FEqFERsvUBNddvfCkfx9JoMlq9ATNBQLxkK4lJPF4vMcFpkiCStOEt0MDJM80NbgPAqZEAQuDzygaiy8owaGiOVIj0h0ZMzLHNPzf5flGYqK6D2LvGRZlEIESavULk1Eug7tuG1DiqxTaDDxDbBGUCDb9ZIaKQAsPXzoEHUExB3J61q-B5KTFJSNch1okMe6sT9fzpQ__&Key-Pair-Id=APKAJCILBXEJFZF4DCHQ'
        img_url:
          type: string
          example: 'https://scdn.veryfi.com/receipts/470e7ab9-3084-4d05-b840-885383a2c22e/8247b18a-41f0-443c-bbf4-10814385e097.pdf?Expires=1628185188&Signature=OAaTOHH3KQYlj9pPA0fO50VjQSC8hnJJVvyJZwiGbK-wLw76UF5tWm0XtD5Htp2xx0vXbqJINIT7joyLA1dik01qDprgUbuXfcGamPUgJ6xcLOBKBF855bpFepK0Jdr-x9aGnx4EER7Z~CxUgvrv99cuFGuMab2s9gr0DwXHgLTCzVMZ2dOhbbvR8Yw8ADddzoOSPkwc~3PBB6AGla8cTQmSO0EWlq87rPaXWRrOnqnHwv5RqLWzVpODWVLeBYYudE2ZlaO~U7ftHzc0llKl3kffn4hElaDd5a7VoN0V9yKrGa1cCgRyYmFy9qtGsn3XPZutgnnzkB-~p6y0CUr7Zg__&Key-Pair-Id=APKAJCILBXEJFZF4DCHQ'
        insurance:
          type: string
          example: ''
        invoice_number:
          type: string
          example: '98'
        is_duplicate:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        line_items:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineItem'
        notes:
          type: string
          example: ''
        ocr_text:
          type: string
          example: '2004-10-31\n\t8:21 PM\nYOUR GUEST NUMBER IS\n98\nIN-N-OUT BURGER LAS VEGAS EASTERN\n2004-10-31\t\t8:21 PM\n165 1 5 98\nCashier: SAM\nGUEST #: 98\nCounter-Eat in\n\t2.65\nDbDb\t\t88.20\n98 Meat Pty Xchz\n\t90.85\nCounter-Eat In\t\t6.81\nTAX 7.50%\t\t97.66\nAmount Due\n\t$97.66\nCASH TENDER\t\t$.00\nChange\n2004-10-31\t\t8:21 PM\nTHANK YOU!'
        order_date:
          type: string
          example: ''
        payment_display_name:
          type: string
          example: 'Cash'
        payment_terms:
          type: string
          example: '15 days'
        payment_type:
          type: string
          example: 'cash'
        phone_number:
          type: string
          example: '165 1 5 98'
        purchase_order_number:
          type: string
          example: '2312/2019'
        rounding:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 0.0
        service_end_date:
          type: string
          example: ''
        service_start_date:
          type: string
          example: ''
        ship_date:
          type: string
          example: ''
        ship_to_address:
          type: string
          example: '3787 Pineview Drive\nCambridge, MA 12210'
        ship_to_name:
          type: string
          example: 'John Smith'
        shipping:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 0.0
        store_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        subtotal:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 97.66
        tax:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 12.5
        tax_lines:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/TaxLine'
        tip:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 12.5
        total:
          type: number
          format: double
          example: 97.66
        total_weight:
          type: string
          example: ''
        tracking_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        updated:
          type: string
          example: '2021-08-05 17:24:48'
        vat_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        vendor:
          type: object
          properties:
            address:
              type: string
              example: '1912 Harvest Lane\nNew York, NY 12210'
            category:
              type: string
              example: 'Fast Food'
            email:
              type: string
              example: ''
            fax_number:
              type: string
              example: ''
            name:
              type: string
              example: 'In-n-out Burger'
            phone_number:
              type: string
              example: '165 1 5 98'
            raw_name:
              type: string
              example: 'In-N-Out Burger'
            vendor_logo:
              type: string
              example: 'https://cdn.veryfi.com/logos/us/949103001.png'
            vendor_reg_number:
              type: string
              example: ''
            vendor_type:
              type: string
              example: 'Fast Food'
            web:
              type: string
              example: ''
        vendor_account_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        vendor_bank_name:
          type: string
          example: ''
        vendor_bank_number:
          type: string
          example: ''
        vendor_bank_swift:
          type: string
          example: ''
        vendor_iban:
          type: string
          example: ''
        warnings:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/OperationStatus'
      
    DocumentUploadOptions:
      type: object
      properties:
        file_name:
          type: string
          description: ''
          example: 'invoice.png'
        file:
          type: string
          description: ''
          format: binary
        file_data:
          type: string
          description: ''
          example: 'image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgYAAAAAMAAWgmWQ0AAAAASUVORK5CYII='
        file_url:
          type: string
          description: 'Publicly accessible URL to a file, e.g. "https://cdn.example.com/receipt.jpg".'
          example: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/veryfi/veryfi-python/master/tests/assets/receipt_public.jpg'
        file_urls:
          type: array
          description: 'List of publicly accessible URLs to multiple files, e.g. ["https://cdn.example.com/receipt1.jpg", "https://cdn.example.com/receipt2.jpg"].'
          items:
            type: string
            example: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/veryfi/veryfi-python/master/tests/assets/receipt_public.jpg'
          
        auto_delete:
          type: integer
          description: 'Delete this document from Veryfi after data has been extracted.'
          example: 1
        boost_mode:
          type: integer
          description: 'Flag that tells Veryfi whether boost mode should be enabled. When set to `1`, Veryfi will skip data enrichment steps, but will process the document faster. Default value for this flag is `0`.'
          example: 1
        confidence_details:
          type: integer
          description: 'Return prediction scores along with values'
          example: 1
        async:
          type: integer
          description: '123'
          example: 1
        external_id:
          type: string
          description: 'Optional custom document identifier. Use this if you would like to assign your own ID to documents.'
          example: '123456789'
        max_pages_to_process:
          type: integer
          description: 'When sending a long document to Veryfi for processing, this parameter controls how many pages of the document will be read and processed, starting from page 1.'
          example: 10
        tags:
          type: array
          description: 'List of tags'
          items:
            type: string
            example: 'tag1'
        categories:
          type: array
          description: 'List of categories to use when categorizing the document'
          items:
            type: string
          example:
           - 'Advertising & Marketing'
           - 'Automotive'
           - 'Bank Charges & Fees'
           - 'Legal & Professional Services'
           - 'Insurance'
           - 'Meals & Entertainment'
           - 'Office Supplies & Software'
           - 'Taxes & Licenses'
           - 'Travel'
           - 'Automotive'
           - 'Rent & Lease'
           - 'Repairs & Maintenance'
           - 'Payroll'
           - 'Utilities'
           - 'Job Supplies'
           - 'Grocery'
      
    OperationStatus:
      type: object
      properties:
        status:
          type: string
        message:
          type: string
        error:
          type: string
        
  parameters:
    DocumentId:
      name: document_id
      in: path
      description: ID of the document.
      required: true
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
        
    LineItemId:
      name: line_item_id
      in: path
      description: ID of the line item.
      required: true
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
        
    TagId:
      name: tag_id
      in: path
      description: ID of the tag
      required: true
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
        
    Query:
      name: q
      in: query
      description: Query request to search in document's `ocr_text`.
      schema:
        type: string
        
    Tag:
      name: tag
      in: query
      description: Tag to search.
      schema:
        type: string
        
    ExternalId:
      name: external_id
      in: query
      description: External Id to search.
      schema:
        type: string
        
    CreatedGte:
      name: created__gte
      in: query
      description: Start date to search(including it).
      schema:
        type: string
        format: date-time
        
    CreatedGt:
      name: created__gt
      in: query
      description: Start date to search(including it).
      schema:
        type: string
        format: date-time
        
    CreatedLte:
      name: created__lte
      in: query
      description: End date to search(including it).
      schema:
        type: string
        format: date-time
        
    CreatedLt:
      name: created__lt
      in: query
      description: End date to search(including it).
      schema:
        type: string
        format: date-time
        
    ReturnAuditTrail:
      name: return_audit_trail
      in: query
      description: ''
      schema:
        type: string
        
  requestBodies:
    DocumentUploadOptions:
      description: Processing Settings.
      required: true
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/DocumentUploadOptions'
            
        multipart/form-data:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/DocumentUploadOptions'
                
    Document:
      description: Document.
      required: true
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Document'
                
    LineItem:
      description: LineItem.
      required: true
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineItem'
                
    Tag:
      description: Tag.
      required: true
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tag'
        
  responses:
    Documents:
      description: List of documents.
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Document'
    Document:
      description: Document.
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Document'
    LineItems:
      description: List of line items.
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              line_items:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineItem'
            required:
            - line_items
    LineItem:
      description: LineItem.
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineItem'
    Tags:
      description: List of tags
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              tags:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tag'
            required:
            - tags
    Tag:
      description: Tag.
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tag'
    OperationStatus:
      description: OperationStatus.
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/OperationStatus'
            
  securitySchemes:
    ClientId:
      type: apiKey
      in: header
      name: CLIENT-ID
      
    Authorization:
      type: apiKey
      in: header
      name: AUTHORIZATION
      description: 'Example: apiKey $username:$apiKey'
